    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    This is a powerful direct damage spell. One draw back is that the bolt is unguided so you need to be lined up correctly or you miss your target.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Research:</B><BR>None<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Direct Damage Bolt
