			Direct dmg spell.  with wis. 134 and <BR>
max evoc. dmg was around 45 pts max.<BR>
<BR>
this is a bolt spell so any objects in <BR>
the way will be hit. also you must be facing<BR>
the direction of your target.  this spell is slow<BR>
but the most powerful for this level.  <BR>
<BR>
PS&gt; also makes a good beacon, as the bolt will <BR>
travel clear across a zone even without targeting<BR>
an enemy, until it hits an object.
			</font>
	
