Also, you must be relatively close to the target.<BR>
Note:* you cannot cast this spell while you are in <BR>
melee combat, it takes too long to cast, so that <BR>
you are either interrupted with your autoattack or <BR>
a successful hit by an enemy.<BR>
<BR>
Warning! This spell tends to make you popular among <BR>
other people's monsters if you cast it, dont<BR>
get too close, unless you like being the<BR>
center of attention.
