		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Make sure your opponent is in direct line of site.<BR>
If something is in the way of the fire bolt, it will vanish.  The opponent can walk in front of an object and the fire bolt will still not hit your target.<BR>
<BR>
Due to the mana cost and casting time of Fire Bolt, it is best used only to lure an opponent, unless you know for sure that nothing will obstruct the Fire Bolt's path.
			</font>
	
