	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			This spell is great for luring and for finishing off the creature (in a group).  Be very careful not to use it too many times on one target though.  That target will soon see you as the greatest threat and start attacking you.  There is little that can be done to take it off of you too.  You can usually get this spell off 2 to 3 times before it even gets to you which is useful if soloing.  This spell is also good for kiting.  If you can get a friendly shaman or druid to cast spirt of the wolf on you, you can fire one or two times, run a bit, turn around and fire again, run, fire, etc.   I've killed lots of yellow conned creatures this way.  If any trouble occurs, just run for the zone. ;)
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
